     H            Y.                                    1
     F** GDLRE3 ****************************************************************
     F*  MATERIAL ORDER DATA SUMMARY                                           *
     F**************************************************************************
     FGDLPP01 UP  E                    DISK
      *
     FGDLWPE0 O   E                    DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@SIRE  4
     C                     PARM           P@FLG   1
      *
     C           LASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     GOTO @END
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE P@SIRE    N@SIRE  40
      *
     C           N@SIRE    IFEQ LASIRE
     C                     WRITEGDLWPE01
     C           P@FLG     IFEQ '1'
     C                     DELETGDLPP011
     C                     END
     C                     END
      *
     C           @END      TAG
